programme.sub-title: South Africa v India: First Test Day Five.

programme.title: Live Carabao Cup
programme.desc: Chelsea v Arsenal (Kick-off 8.00pm). Coverage of the semi-final first-leg encounter at Stamford Bridge, as the London rivals look to gain an advantage ahead of the second leg, which is due to take place at Emirates Stadium in two weeks. The Blues have won this tournament on five occasions, most recently in 2015, and their fourth triumph saw them defeat the Gunners at Millennium Stadium in 2007. Arsenal have lifted the trophy twice in their history, while that loss to Chelsea was one of five times they have finished as runners-up
